text: Mayadyk () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Mayadykovsky Selsoviet, Dyurtyulinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 602 as of 2010. There are 6 streets. == Geography == It is located 15 km from Dyurtyuli. == References == Category:Rural localities in Dyurtyulinsky District
title: Mayadyk
